question: Provide me with a summary ranking of the top 10 processes for each user_id process classification in the system_mods_power_consumption dataset. Rank the app_id by the sum of total power consumed within the user_id, in descending order. Provide me with the ranking number as well as the sum total power consumed so I can have a sense of scale.
sql: select user_id, app_id, total_power_consumption, rnk from (select user_id, app_id, sum(total_power_consumption) as total_power_consumption, rank() over (partition by user_id order by sum(total_power_consumption) desc ) as rnk from reporting.system_mods_power_consumption group by user_id, app_id) where rnk <= 10;
